{"tid":445070,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"依家乜撚狗屎垃圾都賣到成萬蚊圍","createTime":"2017-10-23T04:55:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-23T06:02:30.000Z","uid":36310,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9c3c299c875c55ad697b16c4e4527be5bad5e1c5","tid":445070,"uid":36310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:55:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6wqs2nrm\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6wqs2nrm&h=a2f71a8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n乳豬叫貨300左右<br />\n帶子冰鮮野唔值錢<br />\n花竹蝦來貨二 三十蚊隻<br />\n魚翅 素翅來<br />\n鮑魚都係罐頭野<br />\n條斑會貴啲 都係幾舊水成本<br />\n其餘啲雞 菜飯 糖水唔值錢<br />\n咁都賣成萬蚊圍<br />\n 好過去搶<br />\n<br />\n預計留言:唔撚使賺啊<br />\n人工呢 租金呢 <br />\n食唔起咪出街食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fda5d48260c20049736d8c0a6f53089968d7e1d","tid":445070,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:56:18.000Z","msg":"唔撚使賺啊<br />\n人工呢 租金呢 <br />\n食唔起咪出街食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d45e63ebf09eb00944c32e06753e1e23d466519c","tid":445070,"uid":123224,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:57:17.000Z","msg":"冷氣呢.氣氛呢<br />\n咁上下差唔多架啦<br />\n打個和架咋"},{"pid":"fe75a49738de4da0a5d8708d45f175d27623a9dd","tid":445070,"uid":85659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:58:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔撚使賺啊<br />\n人工呢 租金呢 <br />\n食唔起咪出街食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔撚使賺啊<br />\n人工呢 租金呢 <br />\n食唔起咪出街食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64730b79c505022b3e1c20ed37e2e88cd34424e0","tid":445070,"uid":131259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T05:13:26.000Z","msg":"除非出名酒樓<br />\n唔係既話依圍野貴過六千都唔會食"},{"pid":"133d1d5f5cb98aafe24d9166d87f849a0b82a822","tid":445070,"uid":36310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T05:44:0